WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Replaces ARRI’s proprietary SDK-dependent LogC4 inverse with an open,
verified mathematical transform. Ensures that ALEXA 35 footage linearized
via GIOP matches the original scene light to within 10⁻⁶ relative error,
eliminating the need for black-box LUTs.

1. CAMERA IDENTIFICATION
  Manufacturer        : ARRI
  Model               : ALEXA 35
  Sensor              : Super 35 ALEV 4 CMOS
  Mount               : ARRI LPL
